            },
            {
              question: "Do you use AI and machine learning for image processing?",
              answer: "Yes, we implement advanced AI and machine learning techniques including computer vision, deep learning models, and neural networks for tasks like image recognition, object detection, style transfer, and automated image enhancement."
            },
            {
              question: "How do you ensure image quality and performance?",
              answer: "We implement quality control measures, performance optimization, and testing protocols to ensure our image tools deliver high-quality results efficiently. We also provide customizable quality settings and batch processing capabilities."
